---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Clubs & Groups in Walton-on-Thames — Sports, Societies & Community Organisations"
  description="Clubs, societies and community organisations in Walton-on-Thames, Hersham and Whiteley Village — from rowing and cricket to amateur dramatics and local societies."
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <ol class="breadcrumbs">
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/living/">Living</a></li>
          <li aria-current="page">Clubs & Groups</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <h1>Clubs & Groups</h1>
      <p>Walton-on-Thames and Hersham have a rich community life — sports clubs, societies, arts groups and volunteer organisations.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="clubs-grid">
        <div class="club-section">
          <h2>Sport</h2>
          <ul class="club-list">
            <li>
              <strong>Walton Rowing Club</strong>
              <span>One of Surrey's most active rowing clubs, based on the Thames at Walton. Competitive rowing for juniors and adults, recreational membership available.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Walton & Hersham FC</strong>
              <span>The local football club, playing in the non-league pyramid. Grounds at Stompond Lane.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Walton Athletic Club</strong>
              <span>Track and field athletics club for all ages.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Walton Cricket Club</strong>
              <span>Cricket at Ashley Road — junior and senior sections.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Hersham Sailing Club</strong>
              <span>Dinghy sailing on Bessborough Reservoir, Hersham.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="club-section">
          <h2>Arts & Culture</h2>
          <ul class="club-list">
            <li>
              <strong>Walton Playhouse</strong>
              <span>Amateur dramatic society with regular productions throughout the year.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Walton & Weybridge Music Club</strong>
              <span>Classical music concerts and events.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="club-section">
          <h2>Community & Volunteer</h2>
          <ul class="club-list">
            <li>
              <strong>Walton & Weybridge Rotary Club</strong>
              <span>Community service and fundraising.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Elmbridge Community Link</strong>
              <span>Volunteer transport and support for elderly and disabled residents across the borough.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="clubs-cta">
        <p>Is your club or group missing? <a href="/contact/">Get in touch</a> and we'll add it to the directory.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .clubs-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .club-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(11,36,46,0.08);
  }

  .club-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .club-list li {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .club-list strong {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-navy);
  }

  .club-list span {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-slate);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .clubs-cta {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-slate);
  }
</style>
